-- Russia's VTB says ready to borrow in other markets after Western sanctions
-- 
-- Wed Jul 30, 2014 06:29AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, July 30 (Reuters) - Russia's second-largest bank, VTB <VTBR.MM>, said on Wednesday it was ready to borrow on financial markets outside the European Union and United States after it was included in new Western sanctions over the Ukraine crisis.

